hadiths[10]{hadithnumber,text}:
1188,"maine unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara jihad kiye they."
1189,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen masjidon ke siwa kisi ke liye kajaawey na baandhey jaaein. (yani safar na kya jaey) aik masjide-Haraam , dusri Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid (masjide-Nabawi (aur teesri masjide-Aqsaa yani baitul-maqdis."
1190,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri us masjid mein Namaz masjide-Haraam ke siwa tamam masjidon mein Namaz se aik hazaar darja zyada afzal hai.
1191,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) chasht ki Namaz sirf 2 din padhtey they. jab Makka aatey, kyonke aap Makka mein chasht hi ke waqt aatey they us waqt pahley aap tawaaf kartey aur phir maqaame-Ibraaheem ke peechhey 2 rakaat padhtey. doosrey jis din aap masjide-qubaa mein tashrif latey aap ka yahan har hafte aaney ka mamool (routine) tha. jab aap masjid ke andar aatey to Namaz padhey baghair bahar nikalnaa bura jaantey. aap bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yahan sawar aur paidal donon tarah aaya kartey they."
1192,mein isi tarah karta hun jaisey maine apne sathiyon (sahaaba (Raziallahu anhu)) ko kartey dekha hai. lekin tumhen raat ya din ke kisi hissey mein Namaz padhney se nahi roktaa. sirf itni baat hai ke irada karke tum suraj nikaltey ya doobtey waqt na padho.
1193,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har hafte ko masjide-Qubaa aatey paidal bhi) kuchh baar (aur sawari par bhi aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisa hi kartey.
1194,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quba aatey kabhi paidal aur kabhi sawari par. ibne-Numair ne usmein ye zyadti ki hai ke ham se Ubaidullah bin Umer ne bayan kya aur unse Naafe ne ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein 2 rakaat Namaz padhtey they.
1195,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere ghar aur mere us member ke darmyan ka hissa jannat ki kyaariyon mein se aik kyaarii hai.
1196,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere ghar aur mere member ke darmyan ki zameen jannat ke baaghon mein se aik baagh hai aur mera member qiyamat ke din mere hauz par hoga.
1197,"maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se char hadisein bayan kartey huey suna jo mujhey bahut pasand aaein . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurat apne shauhar ya kisi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ke baghair 2 din ka bhi safar na karey aur dusri ye ke eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha donon din rozey na rakhey jaaein. teesri baat ye ke subah ki Namaz ke baad suraj ke nikalney tak aur Asr ke baad suraj chhipney tak koi nafl Namaz na padhi jaey. chothi ye ke teen masjidon ke siwa kisi ke liye kajaawey na baandhey jaaein. masjide-Haraam , masjide-Aqsaa aur meri masjid (yani masjide-Nabawi )."
